data.description: A charming home, nestled in a pleasant New Braunfels, this 2-story home, with three bedrooms, offers comfort and style, two and a half baths,1910 sq. ft for added convenience. Close to a future elementary school within walking distance and Long Creek High School, it's a treasure. In this vibrant neighborhood, dreams take flight, with a pool to cool on a sunny day's light, a park playground were laughter echoes with glee. A future sports complex, vibrant and grand, where champions rise, united hand in hand.
